snippet.title: Risaaune Baani - Swoopna Suman ( Official MV )
snippet.description:
#risaaunebaani #swoopnasuman 

Presented by : BSK Entertainment & Khadka Groups

Message from Jojo 
Hi!
I tried something new this time. I wanted to give myself a challenge. Swoopna obviously worked hard on this song and the video. Abhinash, you're the OG here. I'm just so happy we got to execute mine and Abhinash's imaginations. 
I'm super super thankful to BT Kancha, Lemi, Irfan Khan, Manoj Maharjan, Prabesh K Shrestha, Foeseal, Ayush Dhoj Bista for happily and easily agreeing to give their time for the video.
Gratitude to all the listeners of Swoopna for sending so much love to him.

Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.description:
JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3 is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll January 2026! Watch JUJUTSU KAISEN Crunchyroll! https://got.cr/cc-jjkpv

Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic - Official Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
Before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen, together. 

When a lost prince is rescued and raised in exile, he grows up unaware of his past. Years later, he returns to uncover the truth about his father‚Äôs murder and his mother‚Äôs imprisonment, and must rise to reclaim his place as the rightful king.

Baahubali: The Epic will be released in theaters across the U.S. October 31st.

#IGN #Movies

snippet.description:

At its helm is India‚Äôs most popular independent artist, Anuv Jain, pairing delicate guitar work with achingly tender vocals that distill this very emotion into melody. Joining him is Indian electronic duo Lost Stories working their magic on the production of the track as well as performing on the harmonium.

At its helm is India‚Äôs most popular independent artist, Anuv Jain, pairing delicate guitar work with achingly tender vocals that distill this very emotion into melody. Joining him is Indian electronic duo Lost Stories working their magic on the production of the track as well as performing on the harmonium.

Listen to Arz Kiya Hai: https://UMGI.lnk.to/ArzKiyaHai_CSBS3


*CREDITS*


Written, Composed, and Performed By: Anuv Jain

Producer: Lost Stories 

Additional Production and Additional Vocals: Sarthak Kalyani

Acoustic Guitars, Electric Guitars, Charango, Bass Guitars: Keba Jeremiah
